{
  "texts": [
    "We validate the performance of LLM agents based on the Car Crash dataset (https://github.com/Cogito2012/CarCrashDataset).",
    "The mobile LLM agents on vehicles are implemented based onTABLE I: Evaluation of mobile LLM agents with different perception modules for different modalities.",
    "ImageBind LanguageBind Model ViT-Huge (632 M) ViT-Large/14 (307M) Image -IN1K 77.7 -Video -K400 50.0 64.0 Infrared -LLVIP 63.4 87.2 Depth -NYU-D 54.0 65.1 Audio -ESC-50 66.9 89.8 IMU -Ego4D 25.0 -LLaMA.",
    "The perception module is developed based on Video-LLaMA, the local grounding module is developed based on LLaMA-7B-Chat, and the alignment module is developed based on ToolLLM.",
    "The edge LLM agent on the edge server is developed based on GPT4 and we implement a GPT named \"Accident Report Assistant\" as the global AI agent (https://chat.openai.com/g/g-7sWJT5dSD-accident-report-assistant)."
  ]
}